trans-unit.source: Represents a subscription to a timer event.
trans-unit.target: Representa una suscripción a un evento del temporizador.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscription> objects are added to the timer queue associated with a workflow instance in order to send a message to a specific <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue> at a specified time.
trans-unit.target: Los objetos <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscription> se agregan a la cola del temporizador asociada a una instancia de flujo de trabajo para enviar un mensaje a un <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue> concreto en un momento especificado.

trans-unit.source: When the time specified by <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscription.ExpiresAt%2A> is reached, the workflow runtime engine sends a message containing the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscription.SubscriptionId%2A> to the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue> specified by <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscription.QueueName%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Cuando llega la hora especificada por <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscription.ExpiresAt%2A>, el motor en tiempo de ejecución flujo de trabajo envía un mensaje que contiene <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscription.SubscriptionId%2A> a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue> especificado por <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscription.QueueName%2A>.

trans-unit.source: The timer queue associated with a workflow instance is contained in the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscriptionCollection.TimerCollectionProperty>.
trans-unit.target: La cola del temporizador asociada a una instancia de flujo de trabajo está en <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscriptionCollection.TimerCollectionProperty>.

trans-unit.source: You can examine <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscriptionCollection.TimerCollectionProperty> and the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueueInfo> objects returned by <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowInstance.GetWorkflowQueueData%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> to determine which activities are waiting on a specific <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscription>.
trans-unit.target: Puede examinar <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscriptionCollection.TimerCollectionProperty> y los objetos <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueueInfo> devueltos por <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowInstance.GetWorkflowQueueData%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> para determinar qué actividades están esperando un <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscription> específico.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.DelayActivity> and the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Hosting.SqlWorkflowPersistenceService> both use timer event subscriptions to provide part of their functionality.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.DelayActivity> y <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Hosting.SqlWorkflowPersistenceService> utilizan las suscripciones del evento del temporalizador para proporcionar parte de su funcionalidad.
